#
# 3rd Edition D&D Random Adventure and 'Game Hook' Generation Table
# by Larry Cormier
#
# HTML-formatted
#
# This Table was designed to generate nearly complete Random Adventures, as
# well as 'Adventure Hooks' that can easily be sprung on your unsuspecting
# characters. The ideas generated by this table can be inserted into the
# middle of an ongoing campaign, or provide inspiration for starting a
# brand new Adventure that can stimulate the creative juices in all of you
# who (like me) enjoy building an adventure 'from scratch' - from a basic
# seed idea!
#
# I've attempted to consolidate several of the Adventure-generation tables
# available from TableSmith, as well as other tables that lent themselves to
# the enhancment of the concept of this table.
#
# Like any Random Generator, some things might not make sense - but then
# again, if you think about it, maybe they DO Make sense - in a deranged sort
# of way! Needless to say, if the situations that are generated by this table
# are just TOO bizarre, tweak it a bit until it DOES make sense... or just
# re-roll.
#
# It's just one more tool to provide ideas for those times when you need a
# spur-of-the-moment adventure fix!
#
# One more thing... I'm not NEARLY finished with this table. I've still got a
# lot of ideas that I want to implement. Look for updates as I implement
# those ideas!
#
